Package: scSeqR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Single Cell RNA-Seq and large matrix clustering 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alireza Khodadadi Jamayran 
Maintainer: Alireza Khodadadi Jamayran <alireza.khodadadi.j@gmail.com>
Description: scSeqR is a toolkit to analyze scRNA-Seq and large matrix files. It performs QC, clustering, DE and visulizations.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0), ggplot2, Matrix, Rtsne, gmp, factoextra, gridExtra
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
